fields.title: Django Meetup
fields.description: A meetup for Django developers and people who are interested in Django development. People of all experience levels are welcome, from beginners to pros!

fields.title: codebar
fields.description: codebar is a charity that facilitates the growth of a diverse tech community by running free regular programming workshops for minority groups in tech.

fields.title: Code your future
fields.description: CodeYourFuture (CYF) is a UK based non-profit organisation that trains some of the most deprived members of society to become web developers and helps them to find work in the tech industry.
